    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use, with no significant scratches, dents, or rust. The paint retains good color and gloss. The interior is clean with moderate wear on the upholstery and trim. Mechanically the car runs well and has been maintained.",
